[src:xla-compiler/basic-linear-algebra-subprograms] It provides bindings to many hardware-accelerated libraries in a unifying notation.
[src:xla-compiler/basic-linear-algebra-subprograms] Moreover, uBLAS focuses on correctness of the algorithms using advanced C++ features.
